import { Send } from '@material-ui/icons'
import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'

const Container = styled.div`

`

function NewsLetter() {
  return (
    <Container>

        <Title></Title>
        <Description></Description>
        <InputContainer>
            <Input />
            <Button>
                <Send />
            </Button>
        </InputContainer>
        
    </Container>
  )
}

export default NewsLetter
